#: frontend/src/metabase/admin/settings/components/EmbeddingSettings/EmbeddingLegaleseModal/EmbeddingLegaleseModal.tsx:48
msgid "That, and we consider shared accounts to be unfair usage. Fair usage involves giving each end-user of the embedded analytics their own Metabase account."
